Hi ozimmels,

You can specify a cookie file in &#39;settings&#39; tab -- HTTP Fetcher: load-cookies-from-file.
File needs to be in Netscape format. If I am not mistaken Mozilla/Firefox uses this format so you 
can use it directly. Keep in mind that our http client only initially uses values from this file and 
they are not locked (they might change during crawling, especially session ids.)

